title: Cozy, Well Kept Home Golf Course Location 3330 Kings
text:
Cozy, Well Kept Home Golf Course Location 3330 Kings ad date: 10/24/2015 
Golf Course Location 3330 Kings Valley Road, Crescent City, CA A lovely golf course just l/4 mile down the road. The home is newly painted inside, has a large two car attached garage with carport and room for a boat. Very private, yard is beautiful and well kept. The loft is very cozy. A queen bed will fit in the loft. One bedroom is on first floor. Cozy with large windows and a great covered porch, all on .51 acre. MLS 1500531 $173,000 Shirley Selman, Agent 785 E. Washington Blvd #2, Crescent City Office Ph: 707-465-2121
